headline.main: VICHY IS EXPECTED TO REPLACE ENVOY; Rist, Economic Expert, Is Suggested as Successor to Henry-Haye in U.S.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Sept. 25 -- The government of Vichy is trying hard to solve the problem of its diplomatic representation in Washington. Notwithstanding a denial issued last week, nobody doubts that the days of Gaston Henry-Haye in the United States are numbered.
